        ],
        "description": "Fetches a bundled resource containing all the lab or radiology results for the patient mentioned in the request. The observations contained in the resource.  \n \n FHIR Resource: DocumentReference, DiagnosticReport \n *  Imaging Narrative \n *  Laboratory Report Narrative \n *  Pathology Report Narrative \n *  Procedure Note \n \n FHIR Resource: Observation, DiagnosticReport \n *  Tests \n *  Values/Results \n",
